Rating: 3
Just took this out of the pan in preparation to garnish....a big thumbs up! Very flavorful and rich--the perfect ending to our Easter celebration. I used chocolate wafer cookies for the crust, since I didn't have any of the called-for butter cookies. Also added some unsweetened cocoa powder {about 1/4 c.} to the cake batter itself. {You can never have too much chocolate.} Terrific!

