Rating: 3
I made this cake for my boyfriend's birthday. People loved it and came back for more! It was absolutely mouthwatering. The roasted hazelnut crust is delicious, and instead of using chocolate covered espresso beans for garnish, I used ghirardelli's bittersweet chocolate squares and a single gardenia to top the whipped cream.